  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/21/dan-morrill-explains-android-kitkat-ota-queue-jump-pitfalls/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/4b0b674c5607d1b241bb59b562a89f64/android-kit-kat.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n手持 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/20/android-4-4-kitkat-arrives-on-nexus-4-handsets/\">Nexus</a> 设备但始终没有等到最新的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/31/android-4-4-kitkat-launch/\">KitKat</a> 升级？没关系，只要清除服务框架数据，然后狂点更新，之后... 等等，来自 Google 的工程师 Dan Morrill 可不建议你这么做。这位老兄在参与 Reddit 讨论时明确对上述做法表达了反对，在他看来这样做的后果很麻烦，清除数据会在潜移默化中对设备的推送通知功能造成影响。当然，这么做并不会让你的手机变转，但 Morrill 的建议，还是准备好 adb sideload 吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/21/dan-morrill-explains-android-kitkat-ota-queue-jump-pitfalls/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://\" target=\"_blank\">Android Police</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.reddit.com/r/Android/comments/1r1n5z/psa_do_not_clear_data_for_google_service_framework/cdiymrp\" target=\"_blank\">Reddit</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.reddit.com/r/Android/comments/1r1dz4/44_kitkat_has_started_rolling_out_on_the_n4/cdiwt6f\" target=\"_blank\">(2)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/21/dan-morrill-explains-android-kitkat-ota-queue-jump-pitfalls/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20773270/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/21/dan-morrill-explains-android-kitkat-ota-queue-jump-pitfalls/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" /